![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/73a4d88c-8a02-42ba-814b-c68a7461be0c/20240408_033242.jpg?format=original)

Matt Hardy has officially become a free agent, according to a report from Fightful Select. The news comes amidst ongoing talks with All Elite Wrestling (AEW), where Hardy had been considering his future. Despite efforts to negotiate a new contract, Hardy allowed his current deal to expire

AEW had reportedly extended his contract through WrestleMania weekend, although the reasons behind this extension remain unclear.

Speculation has been rife about Hardy's next career move. What will Matt Hardy do next?